N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 r. 202.70.33 - Preclusion

State Regulations

Failure to comply with Rules 28, 29, 31
and 32 of this subdivision may result in preclusion pursuant to CPLR
3126. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22
r. 202.70.33. State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
